    "body": "That worked! I was even able to use a more concise syntax:\r\n```\r\n    mainnet: {\r\n      provider: () => new HDWalletProvider(mnemonic, 'https://mainnet.infura.io'),\r\n      network_id: '1',\r\n      gas: 4500000,\r\n      gasPrice: 10000000000,\r\n    },\r\n```\r\nThanks @cgewecke !",
